text.tspan: Life satisfaction is self-reported as the answer to the following question: “Please imagine a ladder, with steps numbered from 0
at the bottom to 10 at the top. The top of the ladder represents the best possible life for you and the bottom of the ladder
represents the worst possible life for you. On which step of the ladder would you say you personally feel you stand at this time?”
